### Automated Testing

Automated tools were used throughout the project to ensure code quality and accessibility.

**Google Lighthouse:**

| Page | Performance | Accessibility | Best Practices | SEO | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Landing Page |   |   |   |   |   |
